name: Dj Game Mr. Crocodile
description:
"Don’t judge a book by its cover."
Someone should be kind even he looked scary, like Mr. Crocodile and his friend. Music unite people and make them amusing.

Inspired by crocodile dentists and Pachinko (Japanese pinballs). A colorful design is accordant with a delight rhythm of music.
Highlights a crocodiles’ll keep eyes on you no matter where you are.
